title: The Incredible Hulk is awesome film in the Marvel Cinematic Universe
review: Hulk was terrible in 2003, but The Incredible Hulk from 2008 film was good and the visual effects and animations was outstanding. Sound effects in the movie was incredible

title: Outstanding for Bohemian Rhapsody
review: I do loved this biopic about the story of the great rock band in music history, Queen and the frontman of the group Freddie Mercury with the top-charted hits like Bohemian Rhapsody, We Will Rock You, Another One Bites the Dust, and We Are the Champions, with outstanding performance from Rami Malik as Freddie Mercury.

title: Joker is Outstanding Film of the Year
review: Best film of the year is Joker, The most outstanding plot and story line in the greatest dark DC Comics film in the DC Extended Universe of 2019.
